'''Bed Bath & Beyond股份公司'''（{{lang-en|Bed Bath & Beyond Inc.}}）是北美的一家家具用品連鎖賣場企業，在[[美國|美國]]、[[加拿大|加拿大]]、[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]均設有店鋪<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/2019/04/13/business/bed-bath-and-beyond-stores-closing/index.html|title=Bed Bath & Beyond to close 40 stores|last=Wattles|first=Jackie|date=April 13, 2019|website=CNN|access-date=June 27, 2019|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130144244/https://www.cnn.com/2019/04/13/business/bed-bath-and-beyond-stores-closing/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該公司設立於1971年，是[[財富500強|財富500強]]企業之一<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://fortune.com/fortune500/bed-bath-beyond/|title=Bed Bath & Beyond|website=Fortune|language=en-US|access-date=February 28, 2018|archive-date=2019-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191231003259/https://fortune.com/fortune500/bed-bath-beyond/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/companies/bed-bath-beyond/|title=Bed Bath & Beyond on the Forbes Global 2000 List|work=Forbes|access-date=February 28, 2018|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129091808/https://www.forbes.com/companies/bed-bath-beyond/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

